<% content_for :title, "Safety Tips - Dealo" %>
<div class="static-page">
  <div class="container static-page-container">
    <h1 class="static-page-title">Safety Tips</h1>
    <div class="static-page-content">
      <p class="static-lead">Your safety matters. Follow these tips when buying or selling on Dealo.</p>

      <section class="static-section">
        <h2>Meet in a safe place</h2>
        <ul class="static-list">
          <li>Meet in a <strong>public place</strong> (e.g. a busy car park, shopping centre, or café).</li>
          <li>Prefer daylight and a location you know.</li>
          <li>Tell someone where you’re going and when you expect to be back.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="static-section">
        <h2>Trust your instincts</h2>
        <ul class="static-list">
          <li>If something feels wrong, cancel or reschedule.</li>
          <li>Be cautious of deals that seem too good to be true.</li>
          <li>Don’t share personal or financial details beyond what’s needed for the deal.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="static-section">
        <h2>Payment and handover</h2>
        <ul class="static-list">
          <li>Prefer <strong>cash on collection</strong> or a secure method you both agree on.</li>
          <li>Inspect the item before paying.</li>
          <li>Don’t send money in advance to someone you don’t know.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="static-section">
        <h2>Report problems</h2>
        <p>If you see a suspicious listing or experience fraud or harassment, <%= link_to "contact us", contact_path, class: "static-link" %> so we can take action.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
